these guidelines are also welcome to attend.  The following are the dates of the training. \par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 Sunday, July 14th - between services in Klein Hall\par
}{\plain \fs24 \f8 Tuesday, July 16th - 7:00pm in Klein Hall. If you have any questions please feel free to contact Cathi Willuweit \softline
