{\plain \fs24 \f8 At Roar VBS, kids discover that even though life gets wild, God is good. Roar is filled with incredible Bible-learning \softline
experiences kids see, hear, touch, and even taste! Craft projects, team-building games, cool Bible songs, and tasty \softline
treats are just a few of the standout activities that help faith flow into real life. Plus, we'll help kids discover how \softline
to see evidence of God in everyday life - something we call God Sightings. Kids will also participate in a mission \softline
project!  Come join us this summer at Roar VBS! For registration forms or more information go to \softline
www.livingsaviorlutheran.org or call the church office at 703.352.1421.\par
